OL,3,CLeiland-James Corkill: 'Love took his
OL,4,Cfirst breath, evil took his last'
OL,6,FAn inquest into the death of a 13-
OL,7,Fmonth-old from Whitehaven, who was
OL,8,Fkilled by the woman who was caring for
OL,9,Fhim, has found "holes" in the adoption
OL,10,Fsystem.
OL,12,FLeiland-James Corkill, from , died in
OL,13,FJanuary 2021 from severe head injuries
OL,14,Fcaused by being shaken.
OL,16,FThe coroner Dr Nicholas Shaw said the
OL,17,Ffailure of the Castle family to
OL,18,Fprovide truthful information to social
OL,19,Fservices was a significant factor in
OL,20,Fhis death.
