OL,6,FLaura Castle admitted manslaughter,
OL,7,Fbut following a trial was found guilty
OL,8,Fof his murder and jailed for at least
OL,9,F18 years, while her husband, Scott
OL,10,FCastle, was cleared of all charges.
OL,12,FThe inquest also heard how much the
OL,13,FCastle family had relied on the help
OL,14,Fof their parents and other family
OL,15,Fmembers, and how this had been
OL,16,Fsignificantly reduced during the
OL,17,Fpandemic.
OL,19,FIt outlined that social care visits
OL,20,Fwere also limited due to Covid
OL,21,Frestrictions.
