OL,6,FIndependent safeguarding consultant
OL,7,FNicki Pettitt produced a safeguarding
OL,8,Fpractice review following Leiland-
OL,9,FJames' death.
OL,11,FShe concluded that "Cumbria County
OL,12,FCouncil followed policy and
OL,13,Fprocedures", adding that his would-be
OL,14,Fadoptive parents were found to be a
OL,15,F"good match" for him.
