OL,6,FAt the time, authorities were not
OL,7,Faware that Castle and her husband
OL,8,FScott were in debt, and key medical
OL,9,Finformation about mental health and
OL,10,Fexcessive drinking was not disclosed.
OL,12,FMs Pettitt pointed out flaws in the
OL,13,Fbackground checks of the couple, with
OL,14,Fparts of the assessment relying on the
OL,15,Fcouple's honesty in declaring debt and
OL,16,Fmedical conditions.
OL,18,F"Much of the system relies on the self
OL,19,Freport of their medical history and
OL,20,Ftheir current health."
