OL,6,F"The system relies on adopters being
OL,7,Fopen and honest about their physical
OL,8,Fand mental health."
OL,10,F"They have to provide bank statements
OL,11,F- a bank statement doesn't tell you
OL,12,Fhow much debt you are in."
OL,14,FDr Shaw concluded the Castles had been
OL,15,F"economical with the truth".
OL,17,FHe added: "It does seem to me in this
OL,18,Fcase, you may be looking at a rogue
OL,19,Fcouple.
