OL,6,F"I feel for those who want to adopt,
OL,7,Fdo so honestly and in good faith.
OL,9,F"I don't know how you can stop someone
OL,10,Ffrom pulling the wool over the panel's
OL,11,Feyes, if they are determined to do so."
OL,13,FEight weeks before she killed him,
OL,14,FLaura Castle told social workers she
OL,15,Fwas struggling to bond and she didn't
OL,16,Fthink she loved him.
OL,18,FA care planning meeting was agreed but
OL,19,Fnever took place.
