OL,6,FThe following day a meeting took place
OL,7,Fwhich showed the injuries could not be
OL,8,Fa result of an accident.
OL,10,FThe coroner, Dr Nicholas Shaw,
OL,11,Fdescribed how Laura Castle had sent a
OL,12,Fmessage to her husband while he was on
OL,13,Fa night shift.
OL,15,FThe message read: "This isn't working.
OL,16,FWe are going to have to ask Penny to
OL,17,Ftake him back."
